        <p class="about-section-text" style="color: #dce0e3">
            My name is <u>Ratnesh Mishra</u> and I am a B.Tech Computer Science student. I like doing Web Development, Competitive Programing and Ethical Hacking.
            I am always willing to learn new technical things. I'll be learning Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning in near future. I learnt
