        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="skill-row">
        <img class="about-img-right shadow p-2 bg-body rounded" src="meme-example-2.jpg">
        <h1 style="color: #ed0f3c">Idea of the Website</h1>
        <p class="about-section-text" style="color: #dce0e3">
            The idea of this website is that a random meme template is displayed everyday. User gets two options, they can either give caption to
            that meme template or they can choose to vote captions given by other users. The image resets everyday and after the day ends, users 
